Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:18.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心中的願望  搖曳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悄悄隱藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:29.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}讓飛雪滑過臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:36.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揮之不去的後悔  緊繫過去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:39.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}北風的細語
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:42.56,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一觸即散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:50.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}寒空中夾雜著寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:58.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}越過了眼中的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:06.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在想給你的旋律  遙指著初星的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:14.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}天空拼湊出的未來  手指間露出的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:22.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}啊  想要實現在此看見的景色…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:28.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:47.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君は今も覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:51.94,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夜の丘に集まっては
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:56.80,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}幼い夢を話し合ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:16:01.92,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}季節巡ってもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:12.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}私たちは「運命」なんてものを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:18.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}振り返ることなど知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:22.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:29.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}星に願いを込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:33.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}想いを解き放つとき
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:38.97,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ah　いつか夢見たあの日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:44.03,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}帰れる気がするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:49.07,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いにしえの扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:53.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}開けることができたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:58.76,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ah　私たちは手を繋げる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:03.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}そう信じていたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:08.64,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}だから私ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}皆の願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:18.58,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}託した光はそして
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:31.74,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}空の一面に今散らばった
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:47.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}你如今是否還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:51.94,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}夜晚集合在小山上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:56.80,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}傾述著兒時的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:16:01.92,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}四季再次周而復始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:12.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們對自己的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:18.82,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}從不曾後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:22.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只知道要一直向前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:29.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向星星許下願望後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:33.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}等到思念解放之時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:38.97,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}彷彿又能再次回到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:44.03,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如夢似幻的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:49.07,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}永恆不變的那扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:53.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}終能漸漸打開之時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:58.76,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相信我們必將會是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:03.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}手牽著手一起歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:08.64,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}所以我才會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:12.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}收集起大家的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:18.58,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}並將它們化為星光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:31.74,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}潑灑在這片天空中
