Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:43.48,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,460)\pos(45,270)}「流星雨之夜」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是由我來做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾我也做一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然沒焦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也在成長嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫諾艾爾來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  托爸爸的福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次來的時候  一定讓她嚐嚐爸爸的拿手菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚可能會晚點回來  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得保持聯絡通暢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點話想跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏雲先生  烏雲先生  快走開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於今晚的流星雨  今年可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也發生過這樣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比那個時候更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道柚季也在強忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚來天文臺集合  大家一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  湊太  之後要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合在天文臺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乃乃香所相信所決定的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯生薑汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要實現諾艾爾的歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  今天晚上大家在天文臺集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天文臺看流星雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不讓我靜靜待著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做多餘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求妳了  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再跟我扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(298,252)\1c202020\bord0\fs10\frz-30}朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明白一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是朋友  妳明白一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳明白一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季這個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡自己的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊太也很珍重自己的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春這個女生  看見別人受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像自己受傷一樣難受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她比任何人都更怕寂寞  有點固執
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻相信只要自己忍耐下去  大家就都能幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我們幫汐音拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用了  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的願望是大家都能開心歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾跟我說  這個願望太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個願望裡面  也包含著汐音的歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟諾艾爾說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  我想大家會集合在天文臺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨  好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家什麼時候會來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  不要擅自闖進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是住在同一個房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在分房了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  分房是在我受傷的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再跟湊太說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季真的可以接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是明擺著的嗎  不跟哥哥說話也沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的要難受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是諾艾爾她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎  呼喚飛碟那天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天早上為了一點小事  我們吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  我們根本沒吵過架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道該怎樣和好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我  向飛碟許願了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和她們永遠好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  和妳也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在湖邊的那一天  我們看見的飛碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想  是不是諾艾爾實現了我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  我的願望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請實現我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跟哥哥  跟大家吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也希望能夠很快和好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  這次該輪到我們去實現諾艾爾的願望了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳  小春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在呼喚飛碟的時候許下了願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我們永遠都能是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我能明白大家的心情  能在大家身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許也是托了諾艾爾的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定會在天文臺等著的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會再也見不到了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如此  為什麼還能露出這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不悲傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也見不到乃乃香和大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當大家高興的時候  心裡就會暖洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當大家悲傷的時候  又覺得陣陣刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當大家歡笑的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾就會想  是不是實現大家的願望了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我和最喜歡的大家一起歡笑著離別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛碟  飛碟  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我能一直喜歡乃乃香和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經實現了我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還能拒絕妳的請求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)\an8\fs20\1c141139\3cAAAAAA}（禁止入內）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們也剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拆穿會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}算了算了  茶都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}乃乃香  諾艾爾  快來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}妳發什麼呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}太好了  大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}怎麼了  又說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}我想給大家介紹個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}初次見面  我叫戶川汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}那種天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.44,0:17:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}在等流星雨的時候來照張相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}大家都來照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}相機借我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}我會全部都拍下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}我們也去拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}不要抖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}必須要好好地…照不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0001,,{\fs22}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經是朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾給我的最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很珍視
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  泡溫泉真愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又大又暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會大家再一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能對乃乃香重展笑顏  也是多虧了諾艾爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.04,0:19:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為諾艾爾一直在守護著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸先生康復了  真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為諾艾爾沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了湊太的幫助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你幫助了諾艾爾  怪獸先生才能康復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也謝謝湊太吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柚季和湊太讓我注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望的真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡做些趕走飛碟之類…過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕對不會忘記諾艾爾的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾也不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香給了我很多很多美好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…必須要歡笑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定  一定要歡笑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道歉  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的話  妳還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  汐音  柚季  湊太  小春
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是  流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來  諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來看流星雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明非常高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該非常高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在歡笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾對大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會湧出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
